com.here.sdk.routing

Enum NoticeCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NoticeCode>
      • com.here.sdk.routing.NoticeCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NoticeCode>
    Deprecated. 

    Will be removed in v4.9.0. SectionNoticeCode should be used instead.


    @Deprecated
public enum NoticeCode
extends java.lang.Enum<NoticeCode>

    Notice codes which point the issues encountered during processing of a route calculation request. The notice codes are going to be extended for new error situations.
